thread.title_full: Autoclick Rent a Car evaluado por ROSALIND

author: ROSALIND
title: ROSALIND
text: The experience was hassle-free for us. We were picked-up by the courtesy bus and the car hire centre was just 5 minutes away. The car was ready for us on our arrival and they even loaded it with our cases. I would use this rental company again and have no hesitation in recommending it.
